16#ifndef RDATA_IN_1_NSAP_22_C
17#define RDATA_IN_1_NSAP_22_C

21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_in_nsap(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 isc_textregion_t *sr;
25 int n;
26 bool valid = false;
27 int digits = 0;
28 unsigned char c = 0;
29
30 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
31 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
32
33 UNUSED(type);
34 UNUSED(origin);
35 UNUSED(options);
36 UNUSED(rdclass);
37 UNUSED(callbacks);
38
39 /* 0x<hex.string.with.periods> */
40 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
41 false));
42 sr = &token.value.as_textregion;
43 if (sr->length < 2)
44 RETTOK(ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
45 if (sr->base[0] != '0' || (sr->base[1] != 'x' && sr->base[1] != 'X'))
46 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
47 isc_textregion_consume(sr, 2);
48 while (sr->length > 0) {
49 if (sr->base[0] == '.') {
50 isc_textregion_consume(sr, 1);
51 continue;
52 }
53 if ((n = hexvalue(sr->base[0])) == -1)
54 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
55 c <<= 4;
56 c += n;
57 if (++digits == 2) {
58 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &c, 1));
59 valid = true;
60 digits = 0;
61 c = 0;
62 }
63 isc_textregion_consume(sr, 1);
64 }
65 if (digits != 0 || !valid)
66 RETTOK(ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
67 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
68}

70static inline isc_result_t
71totext_in_nsap(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
72 isc_region_t region;
73 char buf[sizeof("xx")];
74
75 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
76 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
77 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
78
79 UNUSED(tctx);
80
81 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
82 RETERR(str_totext("0x", target));
83 while (region.length != 0) {
84 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%02x", region.base[0]);
85 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
86 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
87 }
88 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
89}
90
91static inline isc_result_t
92fromwire_in_nsap(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
93 isc_region_t region;
94
95 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
96 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
97
98 UNUSED(type);
99 UNUSED(dctx);
100 UNUSED(options);
101 UNUSED(rdclass);
102
103 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &region);
104 if (region.length < 1)
105 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
106
107 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
108 isc_buffer_forward(source, region.length);
109 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
110}
111
112static inline isc_result_t
113towire_in_nsap(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
114 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
115 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
116 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
117
118 UNUSED(cctx);
119
120 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
121}
122
123static inline int
124compare_in_nsap(ARGS_COMPARE) {
125 isc_region_t r1;
126 isc_region_t r2;
127
128 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
129 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
130 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
131 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
132 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
133 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
134
135 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
136 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
137 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
138}
139
140static inline isc_result_t
141fromstruct_in_nsap(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
142 dns_rdata_in_nsap_t *nsap = source;
143
144 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
145 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
146 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
147 REQUIRE(nsap->common.rdtype == type);
148 REQUIRE(nsap->common.rdclass == rdclass);
149 REQUIRE(nsap->nsap != NULL || nsap->nsap_len == 0);
150
151 UNUSED(type);
152 UNUSED(rdclass);
153
154 return (mem_tobuffer(target, nsap->nsap, nsap->nsap_len));
155}
156
157static inline isc_result_t
158tostruct_in_nsap(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
159 dns_rdata_in_nsap_t *nsap = target;
160 isc_region_t r;
161
162 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
163 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
164 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
165 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
166
167 nsap->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
168 nsap->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
169 ISC_LINK_INIT(&nsap->common, link);
170
171 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
172 nsap->nsap_len = r.length;
173 nsap->nsap = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, r.length);
174 if (nsap->nsap == NULL)
175 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
176
177 nsap->mctx = mctx;
178 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
179}
180
181static inline void
182freestruct_in_nsap(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
183 dns_rdata_in_nsap_t *nsap = source;
184
185 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
186 REQUIRE(nsap->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
187 REQUIRE(nsap->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
188
189 if (nsap->mctx == NULL)
190 return;
191
192 if (nsap->nsap != NULL)
193 isc_mem_free(nsap->mctx, nsap->nsap);
194 nsap->mctx = NULL;
195}

198additionaldata_in_nsap(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
199 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
200 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
201
202 UNUSED(rdata);
203 UNUSED(add);
204 UNUSED(arg);
205
206 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
207}

209static inline isc_result_t
210digest_in_nsap(ARGS_DIGEST) {
211 isc_region_t r;
212
213 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap);
214 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
215
216 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
217
218 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
219}
